'''{{class|Actor}}'''
{{c|native clearscope bool '''IsTeammate'''(Actor ''other'') const}}
== Usage == Returns whether or not the ''other'' actor is on the same [[team]] as the caller. See {{property|DesignatedTeam}}.
=== Parameters ===
*{{c|Actor '''other'''}} :A [[Actor pointers|pointer]] to the other actor that should be checked.
== Return value == Returns true if both actors are on the same team. False if not. When not in a [[Multiplayer#Team_deathmatch| team deathmatch]] netgame, the function will instead just check if both actors have the {{flag|FRIENDLY}} flag.
== Examples == {{noexamples}}
== See also == * [[IsFriend]] * [[IsHostile]] * [[ZScript actor functions]] * {{flag|FRIENDLY|FRIENDLY flag}}
